{"type": "article", "id": 34923, "title": "鞋好看的话，装它的鞋店也得一样酷才行｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-11-25T23:56:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 3000, "name": "店铺设计"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 233, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161125215014Qh0To9VzSOkGIgBc.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><p class=\"\">一店一个样早已不是某些领域的特例了，我们此前就报道过西班牙鞋履品牌 Camper 为其在世界各地的店铺特邀了一批<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/5600.html\">知名设计师操刀</a>。这周我们搜罗了几家画风有些特别的鞋店，各具特色的空间让挑鞋也变得有趣起来。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 18.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Sneakerboy by March Studio</h3><p>踏入墨尔本这家由 <a href=\"http://marchstudio.com.au/\" rel=\"nofollow\">March Studio</a> 设计的 <a href=\"https://www.sneakerboy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sneakerboy</a> 概念店，会有一种进入地铁隧道的错觉。作为一家让用户在线上购鞋前能够在此进行实物浏览和试穿的鞋店，隧道带给人的复古感和高科技设备带给人的未来感结合在了一起：每双鞋子的下方都有一块 LED 屏，上面会滚动显示鞋子的设计师、实时购入情况和买家评论。通过隧道中间的走廊可以抵达试穿区，这里的布局要密集一些，看起来就像是一个图书馆。六张钢椅旁都配备了专用的 iPad 支架，可以直接完成线上购鞋。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611252153329yQZwzr7NqoBiDhm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215334okWBtfmC6EeLu2qw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215334FReyEYAqjfSkpPxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611252153336wD84H1ibnLeTpJy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215332pwCvN7QXPGUJZz1l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>摄影：Peter Bennetts</p><h3>Suppakids by ROK</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.suppakids.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Suppakids</a> 是一家位于德国斯图加特的儿童运动鞋精品店，负责室内设计的 <a href=\"http://www.rok-office.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ROK</a> 事务所为它打造了一面由菱形构成的展示墙，它同时也具备储藏的功能。这面充满了立体感的墙壁还配备了上色的面板，可以随时改变颜色和布局。拆下面板之后，墙上曲折的隔板都留有一道缝隙，供小顾客们滑动木盘滑轮，让购物的过程变得更加有趣。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611252153104O0Hlhg6tCykmJax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215310goRhHwizJ8aBDpxU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751042\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215309yGMqhHW85nBaKR9f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215309Lcj7ZHumYDCoNTxn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215312zy6uUTsDt0eSVEF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FEIT by Jordan Maisie</h3><p>由 <a href=\"http://www.jordanamaisie.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jordana Maisie</a> 设计的纽约西村区 <a href=\"https://www.feitdirect.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FEIT</a> 鞋店是一个利用玻璃和木板打造出的独特空间，给人一种虚实结合的几何美感。站在店外向内望去可以透过玻璃窗清楚地看到层层叠叠的桦木胶合板，很像是一座座高楼。所有的木板都采用了简单的几何造型，利用 CNC 技术切割后先组装成模块再放入店内完成构建。穿插在木板间的 LED 灯点亮后，结合表面的反射，不仅增加了透明感还增强了空间的深度。这套照明系统还可以根据需要变化颜色，打造出不同的氛围。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215228FMi9yfOUAc4lPHLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635697\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215224n3aciGV60LE8yzHB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215226omAQJLjCKfRwOTt0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215228vdC84EhpWAozPVgw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215229iTbkoeJWSuEFMN5l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215228XC96YSGJtWIDK74V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>摄影：<a href=\"http://www.nicholascalcott.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nicholas Calcott</a></p><h3>Little Shoes by Nábito Architects</h3><p>位于巴塞罗那的 <a href=\"http://www.littleshoes.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Little Shoes</a> 旗舰店或许会让你回忆起用来涂鸦的格子画册：负责室内设计的 <a href=\"http://nabitoarchitects.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nábito Architects</a> 几乎用瓷砖填满了这个 100 平方米的店铺，同时利用各种凹凸强化了整个空间的层次感。高低不平的展示架同样由瓷砖铺就，让大小顾客都可以更直观地看到产品。白色和水蓝绿色的搭配带给人一种相当舒适的视觉效果，仔细观察还能在墙上发现随性的手绘图案和文字，使整个空间显得更加活泼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215158jpWndbhqiuI7MlA6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985330\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215158flYgMDUCmNKawzuR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.249389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215159eKzDR0xmn1fJFQwu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.265281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215159bLlYwQc0ianBmVoH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.264059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215157sLcuPv0z5kKgi69J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>摄影：<a href=\"http://www.eugeni-pons.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eugeni Pons</a></p><h3>Run Colors by Mode:lina Architekci</h3><p>为了体现出“奔跑的颜色”这一主题，波兰工作室 <a href=\"http://www.modelina-architekci.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mode:lina Architekci</a> 为波兹南的 <a href=\"http://www.runcolors.pl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Run Colors</a> 鞋店打造了一个由七彩条纹点缀的空间。和彩虹般贯穿在墙面和地面上的直线形成鲜明对比的是店铺统一的暗灰色调，作为隔断穿插在灰色展示柜和家具间的线条让人联想到奔跑时的速度，强调了活力与品牌形象。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215134FnuBXm4AeI6l75DC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215133L62jfNB4vHtcQzpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215134GPpd8cxOh1Vzmone.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215134pE2sxJqlUOGIw8jh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215134DryXUvSK8ZopVd7b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>摄影：<a href=\"http://www.pfmarcinratajczak.fott.pl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marcin Ratajczak</a></p><h3>Camper Stockholm by nendo</h3><p>把鞋放在卷起的纸上？这个听上去充满了破坏感的行为在知名设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 为 Camper 打造的斯德哥尔摩店内成了带给人舒适感的画面。堆在店内的白色卷纸实际上是 2 毫米厚的树脂板卷成的，螺旋结构足以使它们在不借助外力的情况下支撑自己。由此一来，顶部就成了一个个吸睛的展架，加上底部的漫射光线，上面的鞋子带给人一种轻质的感觉，足以激起路人的好奇心。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215059xfhPpi7aRLGO2nuU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.113692\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215058A9Wbc6yIBRChoLKt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215058W7cMFVYziT5s0djv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605134\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215058AhL4FoYbgiwmuqN3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161125215057ZRko7gWvcqA5t6ul.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>摄影：Camper &amp; Joacim Blockstrom</p>"}